metadata.name: Swan Princess: Noir
metadata.description:
When Luna rises, her radiating energy brings out the beautiful souls that hide away during the day. Those who are fearful of dagger piercing eyes. Judgement. 

One of two swan princesses has come out from hiding. 
Noir.

Dimensions: 3000 x 4000 px
300 DPI

Collector will receive CHIBI illustration of Swan Princess: PEARL (1/2 swan princesses in this collection). 
Bidders will receive "Thank you Stamp" <3
